Genitalia
: penis valves with well extended shoulders; volsella short with 12 short setae (Fig. 
13H
); gonocoxa laterally with a few short setae; apex of gonocoxa with acute ventral and dorsal lobes; outer gonostylus circa as long as penis valve base, with robust setae at inner surface; inner gonostylus little shorter than outer gonostylus, slightly club shaped with short robust setae at apex (Fig. 
13G
); S7 (Fig. 
13E
); S8 apex slightly emarginated, with slender setae at apex and along midline (Fig. 
13F
).
